com.diogonunes.jcdp.bw.impl

Class TerminalPrinter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.diogonunes.jcdp.bw.api.AbstractPrinter
      • com.diogonunes.jcdp.bw.impl.TerminalPrinter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IPrinter

    public class TerminalPrinter
extends AbstractPrinter
    This class is a Terminal implementation of the Printer interface, hence all output is sent to standard output. It implements all abstract methods inherited from the AbstractPrinter class.
    Version:
    2.0
    Author:
    Diogo Nunes
